Usage: create_property_alias [-help] -map <alias_propery_name_pairs>
                             -obj_type {pin port cell net clock lib_cell lib_pin design lib timing_path timing_point timing_arc path_group lib_timing_arc si_victim si_attacker lib_pg_pin pg_pin pg_net}

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
-map <alias_propery_name_pairs>     # Specifies pair list of alias and property
                                    # to be associate with that alias like
                                    # {alias1 prop1} or {{ialias1 prop1}{alias2
                                    # prop2}...} (string, required)
-obj_type {pin port cell net clock lib_cell lib_pin design lib timing_path timing_point timing_arc path_group lib_timing_arc si_victim si_attacker lib_pg_pin pg_pin pg_net}
                                    # Specifies Object Type for which a
                                    # property alias needs to be created
                                    # (enum, required)